text: Mohammad Ali (born 1 November 1992) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Zarai Taraqiati Bank Limited in the 2018–19 Quaid-e-Azam Trophy on 1 September 2018. He was the leading wicket-taker for Zarai Taraqiati Bank Limited in the tournament, with twenty-five dismissals in five matches. He made his List A debut for Zarai Taraqiati Bank Limited in the 2018–19 Quaid-e-Azam One Day Cup on 8 October 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Zarai Taraqiati Bank Limited cricketers Category:Central Punjab cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
